  "nodeType": "CHARACTER",
  "description": "Marty's father — in 1985, a spineless pushover still bullied by Biff Tannen. In 1955, a shy, nerdy teenager who peeps at girls through binoculars and writes science fiction stories in secret. Marty's interference forces George to confront Biff at the dance, punching him for the first time and winning Lorraine's admiration. This single act of courage rewrites George's entire future.",
